node.text:
More than the launch of unparalleled works of jewelry craft, @Bulgari's Magnifica High Jewelry collection is a celebration of rebirth. Honored through magnificent muses, music, and Milan, take a look at Bvlgari's latest high jewelry collection.
 
Models: @vittoria, @lilyaldridge @heconghc, @solangesmith and @blesnyaminher
Special Guests: @andreabocelliofficial @beatricevenezi
Project by @oma.eu
Director @tommaso.ottomano
DOP@ mrcodepa
Stylist @sagliogeraldine
Music @guazzonemarco 
Production @studio.april
#Bvlgari #BvlgariJewelry #BvlgariHighJewelry #BvlgariMagnifica #Milan

node.text: After making her #NYFW modeling debut at @ProenzaSchouler, @EllaEmhoff landed a knitwear collaboration with Batsheva Hay (@batshevadress). The 21-year-old student, model, and designer met up with Hay amid NYFW—and #GoodMorningVogue was there to capture their conversations about materials, fit, and texture, plus Ella's rise to fame in the wake of the inauguration of President Joe Biden and Emhoff’s step-mother, Kamala Harris, in January.

node.text: This month, Vogue joined forces with an army of photographers and models all around the globe—stable Zoom connections required, please!—and sent the best and brightest of the new collections via courier services everywhere from Beijing to Brazil, Lagos to Los Angeles. Our concept? Simple, glorious movement: After a year of stasis, immobility and lockdowns, we wanted to see spring fashion breaking free. These are the looks we love, shot by the photographers we adore, on the run and out for a walk, a swim, a dance. Tap the link in our bio to see more.

node.text:
Today, @KamalaHarris became the first woman of color ever sworn in as vice president of the United States.

To celebrate this moment, twelve young women discussing what it means to them to see a Black woman of Indian descent elected to the second-highest office in the land. “Every little girl sees that this is a country of possibility,” @KamalaHarris states in one address, and that sentiment is widely echoed. “She reminds me every day that I am capable and worthy of my wildest dreams,” says one participant.

Director @rombokob
Producer @aliwebb_producer
Casting Director: Rebecca Dealy
Archival Research: Manon Blackman
Editor @ann_lupo
GFX @horatiobaltz
Color @carlosfloresfilms
Mix @cstropko
Post Production @forager.tv

node.title: 12 Girls on What Kamala Harris Becoming Vice President Means to Them

node.text: Throughout the political tumult of 2020, @janayathefuture was one of the most prominent voices to become a source of healing and hope. Reflecting on this week’s events, Khan points out the lack of police presence at the Capitol, a fact that exposes, in their own words, “a clear double standard for how Black protestors have been treated over the past several years. What we know to be true is that there is a way that white rage is celebrated in this country and Black grief is criminalized.” To hear more, make sure to check out Khan’s Sunday Sermons, returning tomorrow 1/10  at 12PM PST on their account.

node.title: @janayathefuture on Moving Forward from the Capitol Riots

Tap the link in our bio to watch the full video.

node.text: “You really start to learn what we would lose with 30 percent of the honeybees disappearing,” says @AngelinaJolie. As a @Guerlain brand ambassador, Jolie was recently in the South of France to preside over the inaugural graduation of the French beauty brand’s Women for Bees initiative, an ambitious program in collaboration with @OFApidologie and @UNESCO that aims to train 50 women beekeepers from different biospheres over five years. Launched in June, the goal is to repopulate 125 million bees by 2025. At the link in our bio, watch the star show us the art of beekeeping—and meet some of the women behind the mission to save the bees.

node.text:
Venice was the place to be today for the star-studded @dolcegabbana show that included fashionable attendees like @jlo, @krisjenner, @kourtneykardashian and more. Domenico Dolce and Stefano Gabbana presented their latest Alta Moda collection by the way of gondolas. Each piece in the collection is deeply rooted in the local artisanship and creative culture of the host city and region, in order both to celebrate the richness of Italian craftsmanship and in order to provide the audience with a site-specific and completely unique experience.

Tap the link in bio to see all the fabulous looks from the Dolce and Gabbana Alta Moda collection. #regram @jlo.

node.text:
In the newest edition of #7Days7Looks, model @palomija walks us through her self-described “wild and wacky” wardrobe. Each piece in her closet is intentional and meticulously considered. From vintage pieces to cool-cool labels helmed by young and diverse up-and-coming designers, Paloma's style is described as balanced and one-of-a-kind.

Tap the link in bio to watch her full week in looks.

Director: @kajal.mov
DP: @rachelbatashvili
Editor: @dpoler
Stylist: @juliocesardelgato
Style Assistant: @theaustenteaparty
Hair Stylist: @evaniefrausto
Makeup Artist: @andrewcolvinmakeup
Gaffer: @WesOrtiz
Audio: @nicmaupin
Set Designer: @not.thestate
Location and Furnishings: @thesomersethouse

node.text:
Last night, @kimkardashian wore the closing look of Balenciaga's acclaimed haute couture collection to reenact her wedding vows with @kanyewest. The event, held at Chicago's Soldier Field stadium, was part of a promotional tour for West's upcoming album, Donda.

Tap the link in our bio for all the details. Photo: @jasonmpeterson

Pleasure, camp, and unabashed kitsch (and attentive, careful preening) were on full display at the Pasadena Convention Center one blistering July weekend. Groom Expo West, "the West Coast's most illustrious grooming show," promises clout, cash prizes and sponsorships—and plenty of furry Cinderella moments.

Tap the link in our bio to see @skylerdahan's document of the event.

Spencer will take place over a single Christmas holiday at Sandringham in the ’90s, when Diana, Princess of Wales decided to end her marriage to Prince Charles. Starring Kristen Stewart, the biopic offers a stunning window into three days of Princess Diana's life, including her bond with her sons.

Tap the link in our bio to watch the full trailer, and for everything you need to know ahead of the film's release.

node.text:
Every year, the Santa Fe Indian Market brings in thousands of global tourists and collectors to the city where hundreds of Indigenous artists from different tribes across North America showcase and sell their new works. 

This weekend, the 99th annual outdoor market returned once again, and the sense of community was as present as ever. At the link in our bio, take a look at the highlights from the weekend–including the incredible style moments captured. Photographed by Shayla Blatchford
